    "summary": "IFTTT exposes a streamable-HTTP MCP server at `https://ifttt.com/mcp` authenticated with OAuth 2, plus a REST Connect API at `https://connect.ifttt.com` using an `IFTTT-Service-Key` header; its docs also define the tenant-hosted IFTTT Service Protocol API developers implement at `{{api_url_prefix}}/ifttt/v1`.",
